OL,4,CExams altered next year after pandemic
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,6, Next year's A-level and GCSEs in
OL,7, England are likely to face
OL,8, "adjustments" to be fairer to pupils
OL,9, disrupted by the pandemic, the
OL,10, education secretary has told MPs.
OL,12,FGavin Williamson said exams in 2022
OL,13,Fwould need to be altered so that pupils
OL,14,Fwould not be at a disadvantage.
OL,16,FThis summer's exams have been cancelled
OL,17,F- but he said the expectation was for
OL,18,Fmodified exams to run next year.
OL,20,F"We very much hope and intend exams
OL,21,Fwill go ahead in 2022," he said.
